    • Constructor Detail

      • Wcs100TileFactory

        public Wcs100TileFactory(java.lang.String serviceAddress,
                         java.lang.String coverage)
        Constructs a WCS Get Coverage URL builder with the specified WCS service address and coverage. The generated URL will be pursuant to version 1.0.0 WCS specification and use image/tiff as the format and EPSG:4326 as the coordinate reference system.
        Parameters:
        serviceAddress - the WCS service address
        coverage - the WCS coverage name
        Throws:
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - If any of the parameters are null
